<br>
Grab 500PP out of your bank.<br>
<br>
Grab a friend of the class that compliments yours for duoing (monk/cleric, necro/druid, you get the idea).<br>
<br>
Go to LoIO, start killing Deepwater Gobos...not alot of exp past level 48 or so, but its something to do, right?<br>
<br>
Every 5 mins or so, /auc WTB Bracer of the Hidden from Bodyguard in Sarnak Fort<br>
<br>
Within 30 mins or so, you should have a brand new Bracer of the Hidden and some happy lowbie won't have to worry about where the cash for their next armor/weapon/spell upgrade is gonna come from.<br>
<br>
Beats the hell out of sitting in NFP for a week hoping to find someone that has one cause, let's face it, the majority of the people who read these boards are at the level where they a) won't be fighting in LoIO and b) want to keep theirs if they have one already. <p>Higar Mettlebender <BR>
